<topic id="preferences-certificates">
  <title>XML Signing Certificates Preferences</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Preferences<indexterm>XML Signing Certificates</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Certificates preferences</indexterm>
        <indexterm>Signing XML document preferences</indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_b4q_bgk_54b"><ph keyref="product"/> provides two types of <xref keyref="glossentry_keystore"
          ><term>keystores</term></xref> for certificates that are used for digital signatures of
      XML documents: Java Keystore (<uicontrol>JKS</uicontrol>) and Public-Key Cryptography
      Standards version 12 (<uicontrol>PKCS-12</uicontrol>). A <term>keystore</term> file is
      protected by a password. To configure a certificate <term>keystore</term>, <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/> and go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>XML</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>XML Signing Certificates</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>. You can customize the following parameters of a <term>keystore</term>:</p>
    <p id="p_c4q_bgk_54b">
      <fig product="editor author developer" id="fig_d4q_bgk_54b">
        <title>Certificates Preferences Panel</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_certificates.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_e4q_bgk_54b">
      <fig product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse" id="fig_f4q_bgk_54b">
        <title>Certificates Preferences Panel</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_certificates.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <ul id="ul_g4q_bgk_54b">
      <li id="li_h4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Keystore type</uicontrol> - The type of <xref keyref="glossentry_keystore"
            ><term>keystore</term></xref> that <ph keyref="product"/> uses
          (<uicontrol>JKS</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>PKCS-12</uicontrol>).</li>
      <li id="li_i4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Keystore file</uicontrol> - The location of the imported file.</li>
      <li id="li_j4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Keystore password</uicontrol> - The password that is used for protecting the
        privacy of the stored keys.</li>
      <li id="li_k4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Certificate alias</uicontrol> - The alias used for storing the key entry (the
        certificate or the private key) inside the <xref keyref="glossentry_keystore"
            ><term>keystore</term></xref>.</li>
      <li id="li_l4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Private key password</uicontrol> - The private key password of the certificate
        (required only for JKS <xref keyref="glossentry_keystore"
        ><term>keystores</term></xref>).</li>
      <li id="li_m4q_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><uicontrol>Validate</uicontrol> - Click this button to verify the configured <xref
          keyref="glossentry_keystore"><term>keystore</term></xref> and the validity of the
        certificate.</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
